snippet.title: Converting measurements - metric distance made easy
snippet.description: It is easy to convert metric lengths - from kilometres to metres to centimtres to millimetres. Learn how to do this instantly. To donate to the tecmath channel:  https://paypal.me/tecmath?locale.x=en_AU
